// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0361 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 16557f20-cb32-55a8-a3f9-d0c525165fc3

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
